data.title: Japanese Surnames
data.meta_description: Japanese Surnames - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides submissions of Japanese surnames from website users, along with brief definitions and meanings in Japanese. The surnames range from common ones like Akai and Akimoto to more rare names such as Aikuchi and Aisaka. The accuracy of the name definitions cannot be guaranteed as they are contributed by users rather than experts.
